VRC+ can only be purchased in-client through the VRC+ tab at the bottom right of the [[Special:MyLanguage/Quick Menu|Quick Menu]], and [[Special:MyLanguage/Main Menu|Main Menu]]. VRC+ is available on Steam, Meta Quest Store, Pico, Google Play, and iOS devices.
</div>

